OL,6,FFootage has been released of a
OL,7,Freckless driver drifting around a
OL,8,Froundabout at an illegal car meet in
OL,9,FSouthampton.
OL,11,FToby Clarkson, 23, from Surrey has
OL,12,Fbeen banned from the roads after being
OL,13,Fcaught driving his white BMW
OL,14,Fdangerously as hundreds of people
OL,15,Fwatched on.
OL,17,FThe illegal event, which took place in
OL,18,FSeptember last year, began in
OL,19,FWinchester, before moving on to
OL,20,FSouthampton, Eastleigh, Chandler's
OL,21,FFord, Fareham and Southsea.
