OL,6,FJay Jones organises legitimate car
OL,7,Fevents and works with the police to
OL,8,Feducate young drivers.
OL,10,FHe said: "You want to go along and
OL,11,Fshow off because you see all the
OL,12,Fcameras and a lot of people go along
OL,13,Fand they get forced in or encouraged
OL,14,Fto show off, and that's where things
OL,15,Fgo wrong.
OL,17,F"You have the choice to go to other
OL,18,Fplaces or more sanctioned events where
OL,19,Fyou can still be respectful and still
OL,20,Fappreciate these vehicles, and enjoy
OL,21,Fyourself."
