OL,6,FThe illegal car meet in Southampton in
OL,7,FSeptember 2024 is still being
OL,8,Finvestigated.
OL,10,FPolice say they will not tolerate
OL,11,Fillegal street racing that puts lives
OL,12,Fat risk.
OL,14,FEmma Hart said: "'We've listened to
OL,15,Four communities in Hampshire and the
OL,16,FIsle of Wight, and they've been really
OL,17,Fclear. This type of anti-social car
OL,18,Fmeet is impacting their quality of
OL,19,Flife. And we've listened and we've now
OL,20,Fdealt with it.
